{
  "stem": "16930.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They forgot that there is a God and-- that there is a God and that God had destined for the Jewish people to get the land of Israel, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And by all calculation, they should never have gotten it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There was no way possibly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They had nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they had a few Piper Cub-- Piper Cub planes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "These are two-seater planes, little light-wing two-seater planes people use for sport or for-- you know, for sport, for just for flying around for hobbies.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They had a few of those.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And-- and-- and at one point they were taking trucks or-- or tractors and putting around them to make it look-- wood around them, you know, fit them with wood around, make it look like a tank.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Of course, a tractor had these tractor wheels like a trank-- like a tank.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So when they moved forward, the Arabs thought a lot of tanks coming in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they had these things, these same tractors going up on ships, up and down, all day and all night.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So the Arabs are thinking there are hundreds of tanks coming in, you know, when it was just these regular tractors used for farm work with a wooden facade around them built to make it look like a tank.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And they had nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the Arabs should have taken it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were pretty close in getting it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were right close to Tel Aviv.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Egyptian air force was bombing Tel Aviv.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- but by the grace of God-- after the [NON-ENGLISH], the grace of God, it didn't happen.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What was your involvement when you arrived in Israel?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My involvement, I first of all was-- went to my kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had a kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we went to hakhshara in-- with that kibbutz, those people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
